2011;;Cloudburst;;Canadian;;Thom Fitzgerald;;Olympia Dukakis, Brenda Fricker;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cloudburst_(2011_film);;Stella (Dukakis) and Dotty (Fricker) are a lesbian couple from Maine who embark on a Thelma and Louise-style road trip to Nova Scotia to get married after Dotty is moved into a nursing home by her granddaughter.[1] Along the way they pick up Prentice (Ryan Doucette), a hitchhiker travelling home to Nova Scotia to visit his dying mother, and the three bond deeply as they travel.[2]